trans-unit.source: Contains information about an ink gesture.
trans-unit.target: Contém informações sobre um gesto de tinta digital.

trans-unit.source: A GestureRecognitionResult contains an <xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture> and the level of likeliness that the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer> correctly identified the gesture.
trans-unit.target: Um GestureRecognitionResult contém um <xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>e o nível de likeliness que o <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer>identificadas corretamente o gesto.</xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.RecognitionConfidence%2A> property to determine the level of likeliness that the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer> correctly identified the gesture.
trans-unit.target: Utilize o <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.RecognitionConfidence%2A>propriedade para determinar o nível de likeliness que o <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer>identificadas corretamente o gesto.</xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.RecognitionConfidence%2A>
Obtém o gesto de tinta digital reconhecido.
O gesto de tinta digital reconhecido.

trans-unit.source: Gets the level of confidence that the <xref href="System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer"></xref> has in the recognition of the gesture.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o nível de confiança de que o <xref href="System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer"> </xref> tem o reconhecimento do gesto.
